We partner with small, family-owned farms that share our commitment to exceptional quality, to bring you delicious farm-fresh milk with no rBST or growth hormones.   What is Ultra-Filtered Milk? How do we make real milk even better?  We start with the freshest milk from family farms we trust.  Next, the milk is filtered to remove 40% of the sugar of regular milk, while concentrating the protein and calcium. Then, lactase enzyme is added to remove any remaining lactose.  The result is a deliciously creamy, lactose-free milk that everyone can love.  No significant difference has been shown in milk derived from artificial growth hormone-treated and non-treated cows.  Our Farmers Pledge: From cows not treated with artificial growth hormones.  This Ultra-Filtered Fat Free Milk has 7g total sugars per serving compared to Wegmans Brand regular Fat Free Milk with 12g total sugars per serving.  Protein increased from 8g to 14g per serving.
